MolMod 0.001 README
===================

Contents of this README File:
 * Short description
 * Software dependencies
 * How to install
 * How to get technical support
 * Become a registered user
 * Author


Short description
-----------------

MolMod is a python package that is used by Zeobuilder. Zeobuilder is a GUI
toolkit for the interactive construction of complex molecular models. MolMod
groups a series of modules that are usefull for analyzing molecular modeling
simulations, and for setting op complex input files. MolMod can also be used as
a library for batch work, independent of Zeobuilder.

More information about MolMod can be found on the Zeobuilder website:
https://molmod.UGent.be/zeobuilder


License
